 * [[http://people.freedesktop.org/~mccann/doc/ConsoleKit/ConsoleKit.html|Latest ConsoleKit documentation]]

 * [[http://people.freedesktop.org/~mccann/talks/guadec-multiuser.pdf|Building a Modern Multi-User Desktop (GUADEC 2007) - PDF]]
