=== GIT ===

There are [[http://freedesktop.org/wiki/Infrastructure/git|guides for using git with freedesktop.org projects]]. There is also another tutorial at [[http://www-128.ibm.com/developerworks/linux/library/l-git/|IBM Developerworks site]]. You can also take a look at [[http://gitweb.freedesktop.org/?p=ConsoleKit.git;a=blob;f=HACKING]].

=== Dependencies ===
     * Linux / Solaris 11+ / FreeBSD 
     * dbus 0.61 (or later)
     * glib + gobject 2.6.0 (or later)
     * Xlib

==== Optional Dependencies ====
     * PAM
     * inotify
 
